22 (b) Query the electronic monitoring system established in KRS 218A.202 for all
23 available data on the patient for the twelve (12) month period immediately
24 preceding the patient encounter and appropriately utilize that data in the
25 evaluation and treatment of the patient;
26 (c) Make a written plan stating the objectives of the treatment and further
27 diagnostic examinations required;
