5 5. The prescription for a Schedule II controlled substance is prescribed as
6 part of a narcotic treatment program licensed by the Cabinet for Health
7 and Family Services;
8 6. The prescription for a Schedule II controlled substance is prescribed to
9 treat pain following a major surgery or the treatment of significant
10 trauma, as defined by the state licensing board in consultation with the
